successes.title: QU-BD One Up - Open Source Production Ready 3D Printer
successes.description: The QU-BD One Up is the least expensive, production ready, high quality 3D printer available on the market! ...Its OPEN SOURCE TOO!

Pledges.description: A laser cut acrylic QU-BD Keychain to show your support!  Thank you so much!

The complete QU-BD One Up as an easy to assemble kit!  The One Up 3D Printer has a ~100x100x125mm build area.  A perfect gift for the hobbyist in your life!  Includes a small amount of filament to get you going!
